results.title: NextEra Energy announces sale of equity units
results.content: NextEra Energy, Inc. (NYSE: NEE) announced today that it has agreed to sell $1.5 billion of equity units to JP Morgan, Mizuho and Goldman Sachs & Co. LLC.
